prompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor painting of a very scruffy, happy-go-lucky terrier-mix dog, mid-leap, trying to catch a half-eaten birthday cupcake that is flying through the air, leaving a trail of frosting and sprinkles. The dog's ears are flopping, its tongue is out, and it has a look of pure, chaotic joy. Splatters of colorful frosting dot the dog's fur and the background. In the center, elegantly integrated into the scene, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The style is flat 2D cartoon art rendered in a soft watercolor aesthetic, with visible paper texture, organic paint bleeds, and artistic brush strokes, creating a funny and lighthearted scene.
